{"remainingRequest":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/understandable/text-understandable.md?vue&type=template&id=071ecf46&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/understandable/text-understandable.md","mtime":1540958169776},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":1533872387000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"网页内容可理解\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#网页内容可理解\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 网页内容可理解</h1>\n<h2 id=\"描述\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#描述\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 描述</h2>\n<p>为了保证用户（包括非专业用户、低等教育水平的用户）能够更轻松更容易的阅读和使用，网页内容必须具有足够的可理解性。此外，足够的可理解性还有助于用户更快的在页面中找到自己感兴趣或者有用的内容，提升快感。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#例子\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 例子</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>html指定lang属性</p>\n<!--beforebegin--><div class=\"language-html extra-class\"><!--afterbegin--><pre v-pre class=\"language-html\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n...\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<!--beforeend--></div><!--afterend--></li>\n<li>\n<p>百度百科对专有名词都会外链到具体的定义页面</p>\n  <img src=\"https://agroup-bos.su.bcebos.com/d4648be59c13a9051044f5dd4df54b53151feea7\" alt=\"百度百科\" width=\"250\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指导建议\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#指导建议\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 指导建议</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>给html设置lang属性，以确认网页的默认语言</li>\n<li>对不常用的比较生僻或者专业的词汇或者短语加以注释</li>\n<li>缩写给出解释</li>\n<li>当文本中排除专有名词、标题，仍需要初中教育水平以上的阅读能力时，提供补充内容，或者提供不高于初中教育水平既能阅读的版本</li>\n<li>如果在上下文中不知道发音的情况下单词的含义模棱两可，那么需要给出发音</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#相关文档\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 相关文档</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG20/quickref/#meaning\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">W3C Web Accessibility<OutboundLink/></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",null]}